channel.title: Santa
channel.description:
Just for those that didn't get to see much of the runescape santa - Here he is.
[IMG]http://i219.photobucket.com/albums/cc76/MrPotatoHead2/santa.jpg[/img]
Metasequoia Model : http://uppit.com/TME38V Delete everything except santastanding if you want to kill him as an NPC.
If you didn't notice already. There are only 4 reindeer and 2 presents, this is due to the economic recession. Santa's elves have gone on strike over pay and conditions. As for the 4 missing reindeer, well reindeer have to eat something. :D
And why didn't we get the santa coif that's in the cache?
Original models by jagex, used with permission - HONEST :) (it's christmas - i'm bored)
